				<h2>Answer</h2>
				<h3>Score ::2</h3>
				<p><p>Basically flags are for things where the normal tools cannot fix the issue. In this case, an edit handled it which is why the flag was declined. </p>

<p>Keep in mind, when we review flags we see the current post and not the original. The behavior was both rude and offensive so I've suspended the account in question temporarily. </p>
</p><br>
